Title: Workflows & Commands

- **Shell**: Use `flox` when available: `flox activate -- bash -c "<command>"`.
- **Non-interactive**: Always pass flags to avoid prompts. Append `| cat` if pager.
- **Background jobs**: Run long-lived jobs in background in dev.
- **Env**: Use `.env.local`. Document required vars in `env.example`.
- **Scripts**: Keep npm scripts small, composable. Avoid global CLIs.
- **Migrations**: Generate + apply in CI preview; gated in prod.

Examples

```bash
flox activate -- bash -c "pnpm i --frozen-lockfile"
```

```bash
flox activate -- bash -c "pnpm lint && pnpm test"
```

